video.title: Sailor Moon Crystal
video.synopsis: Middle schooler Usagi Tsukino and her friends learn that they have the power to transform into Sailor Guardians, protecting the world from darkness.

episodes.synopsis: 14-year-old Usagi Tsukino receives a mysterious brooch from a black cat with a crescent moon on its forehead.
episodes.title: Act. 1 Usagi - Sailor Moon

episodes.synopsis: Usagi befriends Ami Mizuno, a gifted student with an IQ of 300. But something strange and suspicious is happening at Ami’s cram school...
episodes.title: Act. 2 Ami -Sailor Mercury

episodes.synopsis: Usagi meets a beautiful raven-haired shrine maiden named Rei Hino after hearing an unsettling rumor about a local bus.
episodes.title: Act. 3 Rei - Sailor Mars

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends sneak into Princess D’s ball after realizing that the crown jewel of Kingdom D could be the Legendary Silver Crystal.
episodes.title: Act. 4 Masquerade

episodes.synopsis: There’s a rumor going around school that men keep disappearing at a bridal shop. A tall, athletic girl named Makoto Kino transfers to Usagi’s school.
episodes.title: Act. 5 Makoto - Sailor Jupiter

episodes.synopsis: There are reports of a shadowy figure who calls himself Tuxedo Mask committing crimes in an attempt to find the Legendary Silver Crystal.
episodes.title: Act. 6 Tuxedo Mask

episodes.synopsis: Usagi realizes who Tuxedo Mask really is. Meanwhile, brainwashed people roam around Usagi’s hometown in search of Sailor Moon.
episodes.title: Act.7 Mamoru Chiba -Tuxedo Mask -

episodes.synopsis: Sailor V heads to Tokyo Tower for a showdown with Kunzite after saving Sailor Moon from a precarious situation.
episodes.title: Act. 8 Minako - Sailor V

episodes.synopsis: Tuxedo Mask loses consciousness after protecting Sailor Moon from an attack. The anguish of the moment awakens something within Sailor Moon.
episodes.title: Act. 9 Serenity

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon and her friends meet Queen Serenity when they go to the moon to get to the bottom of the mystery behind the Silver Crystal.
episodes.title: Act. 10 Moon

episodes.synopsis: Usagi meets someone who looks just like Mamoru. She can’t help but be drawn to him, but...
episodes.title: Act. 11 Reunion - Endymion

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon and her friends face off against Queen Beryl to save Mamoru from the evil grasp of the Dark Kingdom.
episodes.title: Act. 12 Enemy - Queen Metalia

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon decides to take matters into her own hands with the Holy Sword in a desperate attempt to control her own fate.
episodes.title: Act. 13 Final Battle - Reincarnation

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon rises again to fight against the evil queen. The Legendary Silver Crystal’s power is finally unleashed through the power of prayer.
episodes.title: Act. 14 Conclusion and Commencement - Petite Étrangère

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends search for the true identity of the mysterious girl who fell from the sky. A new enemy shows up at Rei’s school festival.
episodes.title: Act. 15 Infiltration -Sailor Mars

episodes.synopsis: Usagi becomes suspicious of Chibiusa after the abduction of Rei. A mysterious young woman challenges Ami to a game of chess.
episodes.title: Act. 16 Abducted - Sailor Mercury

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends search for Ami and Rei’s whereabouts. Mamoru’s schoolmate catches a glimpse of Luna speaking.
episodes.title: Act. 17 Secret - Sailor Jupiter

episodes.synopsis: Minako sneaks into a “channeling” session and comes face to face with Calaveras.
episodes.title: Act. 18 Invasion - Sailor Venus

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends meet Sailor Pluto after traveling through time and space to Chibiusa’s time in the 30th century.
episodes.title: Act. 19 Time Warp - Sailor Pluto

episodes.synopsis: King Endymion appears before Sailor Moon and her friends to reveal what the future holds for the planet earth.
episodes.title: Act. 20 Crystal Tokyo - King Endymion

episodes.synopsis: Usagi loses the power to transform after being captured by Demande. Meanwhile, Chibiusa decides to go speak to Sailor Pluto.
episodes.title: Act. 21 Complication - Nemesis

episodes.synopsis: Usagi finds Demand’s brother Saphir by a massive reactor during her attempt to escape from the Black Moon Castle.
episodes.title: Act. 22 Hidden Agenda - Nemesis

episodes.synopsis: Wiseman carries out his secret plan as Sailor Moon and her friends continue their search for Tuxedo Mask and Chibiusa in the middle of a storm.
episodes.title: Act. 23 Covert Maneuvers - Wiseman

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon and her friends are shocked to learn who Black Lady really is. Wiseman’s true identity is finally revealed.
episodes.title: Act. 24 Attack - Black Lady

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Pluto takes drastic measures to prevent contact between the two Silver Crystals. Black Lady watches as the consequences of her action unfolds.
episodes.title: Act. 25 Showdown - Death Phantom

episodes.synopsis: The power of the Silver Crystal is released. Sailor Moon and Sailor Chibimoon take a stand against the powerful Death Phantom.
episodes.title: Act. 26 Replay - Never Ending

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon and her friends enjoy a brief period of peace before strange occurences throw the city into turmoil.
episodes.title: Act. 27 Infinity 1 Premonition - First Part

episodes.synopsis: Chibiusa and Usagi suddenly encounter a monster at a research facility after coming across a girl suffering in pain.
episodes.title: Act. 27 Infinity 1 Premonition - Second Part

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends witness a girl performing a strange ceremony in the middle of the night at Mugen Academy’s student orientation camp.
episodes.title: Act. 28 Infinity 2 Ripples

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends visit Mugen Academy to attend Michiru’s violin recital. Meanwhile, a strange occurence takes place at another concert on campus.
episodes.title: Act. 29 Infinity 3 Two New Soldiers

episodes.synopsis: Ami starts a trial enrollment at Mugen Academy after meeting Yui Bido, a girl who holds the top score at Mugen Prepatory School.
episodes.title: Act. 30 Infinity 4 Haruka Tenoh, Michiru Kaioh - Sailor Uranus, Sailor Neptune

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends head to the Mugen Botanical Garden after Makoto develops suspicions about a newly developed plant.
episodes.title: Act. 31 Infinity 5 Setsuna Meioh - Sailor Pluto

episodes.synopsis: The true motives behind the mysterious guardians come to light. Chibiusa’s relationship with Hotaru becomes strained when she learns about her secret.
episodes.title: Act. 32 Infinity 6 Three Guardians

episodes.synopsis: Sailor Moon calls for the scouts who have been deceived by Cyprine to work together. The three talismans resonate together to create a new phenomenon.
episodes.title: Act. 33 Infinity 7 Transformation - Super Sailor Moon

episodes.synopsis: Usagi and her friends are attacked by the Witches 5 when they go to Mugen Academy in order to retrieve Chibiusa’s soul and the Silver Crystal.
episodes.title: Act. 34 Infinity 8 "Infinite Labyrinth" 1

episodes.synopsis: Chibiusa’s soul must be returned to her as soon as possible. The guardians find Hotaru completely transformed as they face Professor Tomoe.
episodes.title: Act. 35 Infinity 9 "Infinite Labyrinth" 2

episodes.synopsis: The three Outer Guardians erect a force field around Master Pharaoh 90. Hotaru fights with all her might to save Chibiusa.
episodes.title: Act. 36 Infinity 10 Infinite - Upper Atmosphere

episodes.synopsis: Super Sailor Moon dives into the abyss in an attempt to unleash the power of the Silver Crystal as her friends run out of power.
episodes.title: Act. 37 Infinity 11 Infinite - Judge

episodes.synopsis: Saturn’s silent sickle has been swung. A single glimmer of light descends gently to the ground as the Sailor Guardians await the end of the world.
episodes.title: Act. 38 Infinity 12 Infinite - Journey
